Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒爆发 不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的仁兄 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们最好也快点逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么样的妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一条大蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间就把城堡给毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条蛇有多大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们村之前也被一条很大的蛇袭击过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条蛇说不定和你遇见的是同一条
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毁掉木叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的回答是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人 这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被这些家伙给骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令弟和叔父大人也一定不希望您这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有纲手大人您的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道您忘了自己的梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也非常了解您的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然您现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实您…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您清醒点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴 静音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不必立刻回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但希望您能在一周内做出决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个禁术需要活祭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,届时请自行准备两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人 我们就地解决他们把
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和纲手大人联手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以解决他们两个的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 我现在很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道纲手的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 他和纲手大人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那件事也...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕见到血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你还是没能克服这个弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血液恐惧症
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该走了 兜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手 我很期待你的答复哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还是晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是大蛇干得好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手已经不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才起就一直急匆匆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 再来一瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人 您喝得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 根本就不见踪影嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑来跑去这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是一点线索也没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先在这里吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是居酒屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说几次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 又没人叫你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼吃些菜就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 那干吗非要在这里吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去拉面馆之类的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报一般都集中在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会跑到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了 真够累的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大姐就是纲手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有50岁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到一天就遇到两个三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还真是个老朋友相聚日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是打个招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位大姐竟然就是\N能够治愈任何伤痛的女忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你 找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就开门见山了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子要求你出任第五代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么好好说到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代已经……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代 果然被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大蛇丸干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲耳听他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大蛇丸干的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他杀了第三代爷爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我一样 是三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 三忍不是木叶的忍者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 他为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼…是九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没说完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸 就是杀死火影爷爷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说他是传说中的三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么知道他的底细却放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她继任第五代火影是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 你给我安静一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管那么多 闭嘴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定由你出任五代火影了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你的答复是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你的弟弟和你的男人复活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我会把木叶完全摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话似曾相识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我以前追求你的时候说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人不是说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她带回村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替佐助和卡卡西老师疗伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在却让她继任火影 到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被人拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非真要跟大蛇丸作交易吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么激动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能胜任五代火影的只有纲手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在可怕的大战时期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她为木叶的胜利做出了许多贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的战斗以及医疗忍术至今无人能敌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她还是初代火影的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上她的个人能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人比他更适合第五代火影这个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她成为火影 就要回到村子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就像你说的那样 给他们俩看病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是木叶的高层 顾问们所决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个下忍就不要多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子跟你以前的弟子不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴臭 脑袋笨 长得也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跟第四代比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都相形见拙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是有史以来最具有忍者素质的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:16:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍术精湛 思维清晰 人气又旺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得也跟我一样帅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是第四代也没活多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了村子 连命都搭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命和金钱不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有傻瓜才会轻易献出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爷爷和第二代 志在平定战乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他们为了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壮志未酬身先死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变了 纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你心里是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你怎么能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说我也是五十多的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岁月是可以改变一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿飞老师也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一把岁数了还逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影根本就是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有傻瓜才会做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 这里是酒馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当着我的面侮辱三代爷爷和第四代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是女人我也不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要揍扁你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够胆量 居然当着我的面挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外边去解决吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说我也是三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付下忍 我可不会那么当真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分钟搞定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一分钟 而是一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付你一根手指足以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 放马过来吧 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹我的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你被我打晕前我想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:20:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么如此执着于火影的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要得到火影的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为火影…火影是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 有空挡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般手段估计赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样 不如用那招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这招是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没这样一起喝酒了 纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没怀念过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你又变漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有言在先 你想也别想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你才没兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都五十多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:22:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有 这样子让我想起了以前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.38,0:23:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初代火影的遗物 召唤死亡的首饰